FBIS3-17960 "drsov062_r_94007" FBIS-SOV-94-062 Document Type:Daily Report 30 Mar 1994 Azerbaijan Adviser Beats Up Human Rights Committee Chairman LD3103001394 Moscow Russian Television Network in Russian 1920 GMT 30 Mar 94 LD3103001394 Moscow Russian Television Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] According to a report of the Khabar-Servis agency, last night, after a routine evening sitting of the Azerbaijani parliament, Neymat Panakhli, adviser to President Aliyev, beat up the chairman of the republic's committee for human rights, Professor Adalyat Ragimli. According to the republic's general procurator, perhaps the presidential adviser did not like the speech by Professor Ragimli at the sitting.
